mbnscMIB.name: mbnscMIB
mbnscMIB.description: This mib definition is used for all MOBATime network slave clocks.

MOBAAlarm64.name: MOBAAlarm64
MOBAAlarm64.description: The alarm list is an array of bytes. The first byte defines the mask for the alarm bits 0..7. The last byte defines the mask for the alarm bits 56..63. Every byte has the range 0 ... 255 (binary).

MOBAFlags64.name: MOBAFlags64
MOBAFlags64.description: The flags are an array of bytes. The first byte defines the mask for the status bits 0..7. The last byte defines the mask for the status bits 56..63. Every byte has the range 0 ... 255 (binary).
